[I] API to create and parse X.509 and CMS related objects

[T] Libksba is a library to make the tasks of working with X.509
[T] certificates, CMS data and related objects more easy. It provides a
[T] highlevel interface to the implemented protocols and presents the data
[T] in a consistent way. There is no more need to worry about all the
[T] nasty details of the protocols.

[U] https://www.gnupg.org

[A] Werner Koch <wk@gnupg.org> (Maintainer)
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[F] CROSS
[C] extra/crypto

[L] GPL
